This file is usr/src/cmd/fma/eversholt/README.

This is the top-level source directory for the eversholt fault
diagnosis technology.  The common directory contains files shared
by the various eversholt components.  The esc directory contains
files specific to the eversholt compiler.

On Solaris, the diagnosis engine is build as a plugin to the fault
management daemon (fmd) in the directory:
	usr/src/cmd/fma/modules/common/eversholt
